  "description": "Admin SPA for clam-cms — React 19 + Vite + Tailwind v4 + shadcn. Platform-agnostic: ships a single self-contained HTML string consumed by clam-cms-cloudflare / clam-cms-netlify mount layers.",
  "license": "Apache-2.0",
